This function performs pairwise alignment of all sequences and compute the score of each alignment

Usage

get_alignment_score(fasta, type, alignment_method, cores = 2)

Arguments

fasta

a fasta file containing all sequences from a multigene family

type

if the sequences are from nucleotide (nuc) or protein (prot)

alignment_method

method of sequence alignment (local) or (global)

cores

number of cores to be used in the parallel computation

Value

It returns a dataframe containing the scores of each alignment
